Enhancement: Preference for locking access from document provider is now independent from locking methods

Previously, the "Access from document provider" preference was only enabled if at least one
locking method was activated. Now, it has changes to "Lock access from document provider"
and is independent from locking methods, just like another preference.

https://github.com/owncloud/android/issues/3520
https://github.com/owncloud/android/pull/3538